WEBVTT

00:28.329 --> 00:30.896
Down, on the ground!

00:30.898 --> 00:31.964
Get on the ground!

00:39.373 --> 00:41.407
Wyatt to Viceroy,

00:43.577 --> 00:45.711
we have a runner, I
repeat, we have a runner.

00:47.581 --> 00:49.748
VICEROY ON
RADIO: Acknowledged.

00:49.750 --> 00:51.884
Pursue runner with
authority to shoot to kill.

00:53.154 --> 00:54.887
Copy.

01:09.703 --> 01:12.104
Double water rations for
anybody who speaks up.

01:16.944 --> 01:18.143
Nobody saw a fucking thing.

01:41.435 --> 01:44.403
If you run, you kill
one of your own.

